{"tid":2293011,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【 「好市民奬」標語創作比賽】","createTime":"2020-11-20T03:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T03:27:55.000Z","uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c3cfc8e44d1a74deec8c8f45050c2e2f3021760e","tid":2293011,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T03:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.facebook.com/HongKongPoliceForce\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHongKongPoliceForce&h=2f8f73b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【 「好市民奬」標語創作比賽】<br />\n一年一度嘅「好市民奬」即將舉行喇！ 今次搞搞新意思，邀請大家一齊為「好市民奬」創作新標語，希望能夠集思廣益，提高市民同埋警方攜手撲滅罪行嘅意識。<br />\n比賽由今日起到2020年11月26日下午5點截止，我哋會揀出20名最別出心裁，琅琅上口嘅作品，得奬者將會獲得精美禮品包乙份，作品更有機會被用作「好市民奬」的宣傳口號。 <br />\n參加方法：將你哋嘅作品，留言喺呢個 post下面，字數不限。<br />\n#集思廣益 <br />\n#齊齊做個好市民 <br />\n#攜手撲滅罪行 <br />\n#有奬標語創作比賽"},{"pid":"39307f698c34bb38bb5aa8f53772d1caf0cf2048","tid":2293011,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T03:02:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HongKongPoliceForce\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHongKongPoliceForce&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BUBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=61f4abe2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HongKongPoliceForce</a>"},{"pid":"4aee6d1280e9e9323b429136b1a0b41026498cc6","tid":2293011,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T03:27:55.000Z","msg":"D留言笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}